{
  "texts": [
    "We chose prostate cancer as our specific use case.",
    "We chose a relatively smaller size for our LLM(i..e, 124M parameters) and collected and parsed prostate cancer related patients' data including clinical notes and radiology and pathology reports for its training.",
    "We also devised domain-specific self-supervised training techniques to ensure that model learned the nuances of the chosen domain.",
    "We evaluated the proposed LLM against similarly sized general purpose LLM (GPT2-small) as well as larger domain-specific LLM (BioGPT) on two tasks; i) clinical information mask prediction, and ii) question-answering.",
    "We also measured the performance in a user study with 3 independent raters who evaluated the generated responses in terms of completeness, correctness and relevance."
  ]
}